Responsibilities

Development and deployment of websites and/or web-based applications;
Implement appropriate and tidy codes and test them in various environments, enhance and/or modify them if necessary;
Follow standardized procedures to ensure the smoothness of development;
Handle multiple projects simultaneously in a timely and professional manner.

Requirements

Diploma, associate degree or bachelor degree in Computer Science, I.T. or related disciplines;
1-2 years relevant working experience in related fields;
Solid knowledge in web technologies and frameworks: HTML, SCSS, jQuery, PHP, MySQL, Bootstrap, Symfony;
Proficiency in front-end development would be a bonus;
Self-motivated, energetic and passionate in exploring new technology;
Strong problem solving, interpersonal & communication skills and team player;
Ability to work under pressure by handling multiple assignments and meeting tight deadlines;
Detailed mind, proactive and willing to take responsibility;
Fresh graduates will also be considered
Immediate availability would be a high priority. 

We offer:

5-day work
Medical Insurance
Young and joyful working environment
Comprehensive training and career development opportunities

Interested parties please send your application with a full resume stating your present and expected salary to the Company.

JOIN OUR CHICLE'S FAMILY. APPLY NOW!

**All information will be used for recruitment purposes only**

Job Responsibilities:

Work closely with both internal and external parties to manage the e-commerce site to ensure the success of all deliverables as per schedule;
Manage new features implementation from collecting user requirements, defining project scope, specification, timeline/resource, and final testing;
Manage third party and external providers’ contracts and Statement of Work;
Track project deliverables and prepare reports defining project progress, issues and solutions;
Optimize user experience on various devices according to best practices;
Constantly strive for new/innovated ideas and solutions for the business & improve operation efficiency of the team;
Propose solutions with options to solve the problems arising out of the website development;
Support ecommerce operation on routine operation tasks

 Requirement

Degree holder in Computer Science, IT or other related discipline
At least 4 years relevant experience in E-commerce website management
Proficient PC skills in MS Excel, Word and Power Point
Experience in Magento is an advantage
Ability to handle multi-task, target-oriented, work under pressure and meet deadlines required
Work independently, self-motivated, detail-minded, good attitude, strong sense of responsibility
Good team player and good in communicating with different levels within the organization
Good command in both oral and written English, Cantonese and Mandarin

We offer 5-day work week, medical and dental insurance, MPF, bank holidays and competitive remuneration package to the right candidate.

All information collected will be used for recruitment related purpose only and will be treated in strict confidence. Applicants who are not notified within 8 weeks may consider their application unsuccessful. All applications will be retained for maximum 6 months and will be destroyed.

RESPONSIBILITIES :

Design and develop the database architecture, including container hosting and orchestration;
Responsible for coding, application implementation, and documentation of the various project;
Conduct data migration and support various types of testing;
Support application lifecycle.

REQUIREMENTS :

Degree in Computer Science, Information Technology or related disciplines;
5 years or above relevant post-qualification experience;
Solid hands-on development experience in Web API development;
Familiar with JavaScript, HTML/HTML5, MySQL, Jquary, CSS/CSS3, PHP;
Creative, Self--motivated, Initiative, Well-organized, Details-oriented, and willing to work under pressure;
A good team player with excellent interpersonal and communication skills.

 **DATA COLLECTED WILL BE USED FOR RECRUITMENT PURPOSE ONLY**
